responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "993F13B9455F7E18AB20C8ABF805BDC5", "Many have approached the Viscount with their problems and he has been generous with his resources. He\'s already given the Waltons several bushels of grain, and posted several guards around the perimeter to prevent bandits from taking over the town. I hear nothing but gratitude for the Viscount.")
